## Problem Description

Sudoku is a logic-based number placement puzzle played on a 9×9 grid. Some cells are pre-filled, and the objective is to fill the remaining cells such that all constraints are satisfied.

This project provides an interactive GUI where users can input numbers and attempt to solve the puzzle. The system can also automatically solve the puzzle and validate the user’s solution.

The program ensures that:
- Each row contains digits 1–9 without repetition
- Each column contains digits 1–9 without repetition
- Each 3×3 subgrid contains digits 1–9 without repetition
